{"3238940": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "和存在感薄弱的妹妹一起的簡單生活", "steam_appid": 3238940, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/3fd6fecf3c60b9428172e9c92ee31c51.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/3fd6fecf3c60b9428172e9c92ee31c51.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——如今已是距離魔王被勇者討伐過去了很多年的時代。曾經聲名遠揚的勇者和賢者,他們的傳説如今也不過成了大人用來教訓小孩的童話罷了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「深淵」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是對十年前突然出現的謎之大型迷宮的稱呼。它有着似乎無窮無儘的深度，星羅棋佈的遺跡，以及受到魔力滋養而快速繁殖的魔物。冒險者曾多次組隊深入其中，卻始終沒有取得決定性的進展。這座迷宮也從未對外展現過侵略或反擊的意圖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最終，關於深淵的一切都隨着時間被人們遺忘，除你之外的冒險者們也不再踏足此處。而治愈妹妹疾病的唯一希望“紅髓液”，就藏在深淵之底。那你是仍堅持每日探索深淵的動力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爲了守護和妹妹一起度過的日常，爲了每天在家中靜靜等待你凱旋歸來的妹妹的笑容——你決心征服深淵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/76132cbe39d4fbe7d37b058c82289840.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=119 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/76132cbe39d4fbe7d37b058c82289840.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一款以妹妹日常爲核心的生活模擬遊戲。所有場景都採用手繪動畫演出、妹妹的每一句台詞都有配音！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在家裡你可以做飯、和妹妹聊天、一起看動畫和玩遊戲、叫妹妹起床、刷牙、洗澡……有多到驚人的生活場景！所有玩法都是高自由度的SLG模式，所有事件都會隨着和妹妹的好感度提昇而發生循序漸進的細膩變化！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在深淵中也不僅僅只有戰鬥，發生的事件、找到的物品都將與和妹妹一起的生活發生聯動，讓玩法更加豐富多彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/5215352a7498c40bb20c6a9ae07a30bc.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=522 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/5215352a7498c40bb20c6a9ae07a30bc.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/53cf3c4f9b552cd0f3f32c6e4d528bbe.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/53cf3c4f9b552cd0f3f32c6e4d528bbe.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/02bbb187da2127bb3de592b52fc73842.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=119 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/02bbb187da2127bb3de592b52fc73842.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>與妹妹的日常</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒險歸來後,你將與妹妹享受難得的溫馨時光——用從深淵收集到的食材做飯、暢談冒險故事、和妹妹一起玩遊戲和看電視，或者並肩小憩。作爲養成繫遊戲,你可以細緻觀察妹妹的成長,感受作爲哥哥的成就感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而隨着和妹妹變得更親密,還能解鎖更多互動！幾乎所有事件都會隨着和妹妹的好感度提昇而發生循序漸進的細膩變化！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>動畫表現</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由在推特擁有84萬粉絲的知名插畫師逆流茶會繪製了大量手繪動畫，擁有與live2d動畫、靜態CG截然不同的生動表現力！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>語音演出</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妹妹的所有台詞都有配音。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike 與開放世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次進入深淵，地形、敵人、寶物等都會發生小小的變化，提供無儘的重玩價值和挑戰。你需要在每次探索中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >學習和適應,才能更深入地挖掘深淵的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ACT 實時戰鬥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲採用了使用鍵盤和鼠標的即時戰鬥模式，你可以通過組合技能和裝備獲取全新的戰鬥體驗。深淵每一層的挑戰都是獨一無二的，你需要靈活運用戰術和技能才能取得勝利。隨着深入探索,你可以解鎖新的技能和裝備，更多的配裝思路也就意味着更多的可能性和更強大的戰鬥力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/db152c9ede1d112bc377c6d22114d099.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/db152c9ede1d112bc377c6d22114d099.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/3fd6fecf3c60b9428172e9c92ee31c51.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/3fd6fecf3c60b9428172e9c92ee31c51.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——如今已是距離魔王被勇者討伐過去了很多年的時代。曾經聲名遠揚的勇者和賢者,他們的傳説如今也不過成了大人用來教訓小孩的童話罷了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「深淵」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是對十年前突然出現的謎之大型迷宮的稱呼。它有着似乎無窮無儘的深度，星羅棋佈的遺跡，以及受到魔力滋養而快速繁殖的魔物。冒險者曾多次組隊深入其中，卻始終沒有取得決定性的進展。這座迷宮也從未對外展現過侵略或反擊的意圖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最終，關於深淵的一切都隨着時間被人們遺忘，除你之外的冒險者們也不再踏足此處。而治愈妹妹疾病的唯一希望“紅髓液”，就藏在深淵之底。那你是仍堅持每日探索深淵的動力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爲了守護和妹妹一起度過的日常，爲了每天在家中靜靜等待你凱旋歸來的妹妹的笑容——你決心征服深淵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/76132cbe39d4fbe7d37b058c82289840.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=119 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/76132cbe39d4fbe7d37b058c82289840.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一款以妹妹日常爲核心的生活模擬遊戲。所有場景都採用手繪動畫演出、妹妹的每一句台詞都有配音！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在家裡你可以做飯、和妹妹聊天、一起看動畫和玩遊戲、叫妹妹起床、刷牙、洗澡……有多到驚人的生活場景！所有玩法都是高自由度的SLG模式，所有事件都會隨着和妹妹的好感度提昇而發生循序漸進的細膩變化！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在深淵中也不僅僅只有戰鬥，發生的事件、找到的物品都將與和妹妹一起的生活發生聯動，讓玩法更加豐富多彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/5215352a7498c40bb20c6a9ae07a30bc.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=522 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/5215352a7498c40bb20c6a9ae07a30bc.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/53cf3c4f9b552cd0f3f32c6e4d528bbe.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/53cf3c4f9b552cd0f3f32c6e4d528bbe.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/02bbb187da2127bb3de592b52fc73842.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=119 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/02bbb187da2127bb3de592b52fc73842.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>與妹妹的日常</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒險歸來後,你將與妹妹享受難得的溫馨時光——用從深淵收集到的食材做飯、暢談冒險故事、和妹妹一起玩遊戲和看電視，或者並肩小憩。作爲養成繫遊戲,你可以細緻觀察妹妹的成長,感受作爲哥哥的成就感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而隨着和妹妹變得更親密,還能解鎖更多互動！幾乎所有事件都會隨着和妹妹的好感度提昇而發生循序漸進的細膩變化！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>動畫表現</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由在推特擁有84萬粉絲的知名插畫師逆流茶會繪製了大量手繪動畫，擁有與live2d動畫、靜態CG截然不同的生動表現力！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>語音演出</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妹妹的所有台詞都有配音。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike 與開放世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次進入深淵，地形、敵人、寶物等都會發生小小的變化，提供無儘的重玩價值和挑戰。你需要在每次探索中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >學習和適應,才能更深入地挖掘深淵的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ACT 實時戰鬥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲採用了使用鍵盤和鼠標的即時戰鬥模式，你可以通過組合技能和裝備獲取全新的戰鬥體驗。深淵每一層的挑戰都是獨一無二的，你需要靈活運用戰術和技能才能取得勝利。隨着深入探索,你可以解鎖新的技能和裝備，更多的配裝思路也就意味着更多的可能性和更強大的戰鬥力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/db152c9ede1d112bc377c6d22114d099.poster.avif?t=1776482346\" width=780 height=311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/db152c9ede1d112bc377c6d22114d099.webm?t=1776482346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "妹同居 X 動作戰鬥 X Roguelike X 開放世界！一款全手繪動畫演出+全語音的妹同居SLG遊戲！父親去世後，你承擔了照顧妹妹的職責，爲了治愈她的疾病，你穿梭於深淵中尋找靈藥“紅髓液”。從深淵中收集食材，烹飪料理，然後和妹妹一同享用，並談論旅途中的點滴……守護這份平靜的生活，正是你戰鬥的理由。", "supported_languages": "簡體中文, 英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文, 繁體中文, 法文, 西班牙文 - 西班牙, 俄文, 西班牙文 - 拉丁美洲, 越南文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/27a692823926c3f5f316bb2f72d90678380ba15b/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776482346", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/87b584af4109bfe62c31e702aabe2448dd4ad0b8/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776482346", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/87b584af4109bfe62c31e702aabe2448dd4ad0b8/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776482346", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2+ GHz Processor<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL ES 2.0 hardware driver support required for WebGL acceleration. (AMD Catalyst 10.9, nVidia 358.50)<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026 第 4 季"}}}}